00:35:22,750 --> 00:35:25,539
♫ <i>Which froze everything between you and me</i> ♫

392
00:35:25,539 --> 00:35:28,619
Didn't you hear what I said?

393
00:35:28,619 --> 00:35:31,579
Follow her and send her back to Central Plain!

394
00:35:33,968 --> 00:35:38,660
♫ <i>My longings become a cocoon</i> ♫

